dct_description_sm: Redigiert von Prof. Dr. J.I. Kettler ; Bearb. von A. Bludau, O. Herkt und Prof. Dr. J.I. Kettler.
Relief shown by hachures and spot heights, depths by isolines.
Legend shows various cities and villages, various locations (lighthouses, forts, railroads, anchorages, old battlefields, mines, ruines, etc.)
Inset map is untitled political map of Balkan Peninsula (including western Turkey and Austro-Hungarian Empire), with color legend.
